Never thought I'd see the day
we'd have bright-eyed kids
studying away in the village.

rows.label: tlk4750016503_msg0002
rows.name:
I think someday, this place
will be prestigious enough to
rival Acedia's old academy...

rows.label: tlk4750016503_msg0004
rows.name:
You're the pride of the village,
you lot are. The magnificent Rex
and his fine companions!
